thread.title: Janet Edmunds

author: Janet Edmunds
title: Janet Edmunds
text: I saw the plate on Sunday afternoon and it was on my car by Wednesday. I made one phonecall and received emails from Regtransfers telling me of the progress of my plate. I received my plates in the post on the Wednesday and was able to have them fitted. I am just awaiting my documents showing the new number. I would highly recommend Regtransfers.
